headline: PPG and FIRE-OFF launch packaging recycling program in the Netherlands
summary: AMSTERDAM, November 13, 2025--PPG (NYSE: PPG) today announced that the SIGMA COATINGS™ brand by PPG has partnered with waste logistics provider FIRE-OFF and packaging manufacturer Dijkstra Plastics to launch Sigma EcoCollect, a nationwide initiative in the Netherlands enabling professional painters to voluntarily return plastic and metal packaging both from Sigma Coatings and competitor products for recycling.
